      "updated_at": "2026-07-10T03:37:11Z",
      "body": "The task queue is empty, and `exit_current` always is retrying without switching to the main thread, bringing the resource exhasusion.\n\nThe fix can be\n* putting the main thread in the task queue\n* or adding a shim to terminate a task, having miri reschedule the main thread\n",
